cast.overview: A CIA operation to purchase classified Russian documents is blown by a rival agent, who then shows up in the sleepy seaside village where Bourne and Marie have been living. The pair run for their lives and Bourne, who promised retaliation should anyone from his former life attempt contact, is forced to once again take up his life as a trained assassin to survive.
cast.title: The Bourne Supremacy

details.biography: Victoria Unikel is a multitalented and award-winning international artist, producer, legendary and shocking performer, creator, writer and a serial entrepreneur with 25 years’ entertainment and business experience. Victoria is CEO, producer and co-founder of Gossip Stone TV, 24Fashion TV, and President and co-founder of VUGA Enterprises Media Group and Edison Aerospace.
details.name: Victoria Unikel
